  "original_title": "\u2019\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0bcb\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd\u2019",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "'Betrayal of trust by Sri Lankan government'",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "India should understand Sri Lanka's treachery in allowing the Chinese ship, says PMC Founder Ramadoss said.",
        "Following India's pressure, the Sri Lankan government, which denied permission to the Chinese spy ship, has now reversed its position and allowed the Chinese ship to arrive at Ambantota port the day after tomorrow. The action of the Sri Lankan government is a huge betrayal of trust.",
        "If a Chinese ship docks in a Sri Lankan port, southern states including Tamil Nadu will be spied on. Sri Lanka has given permission to the Chinese ship even after warning that it would pose a threat to India's security. This is an example of Sri Lanka's affection for China.",
        "India is providing Tornier 228 fighter jets to Sri Lanka free of charge on Sri Lanka's request. In this way, Sri Lanka is betraying India by receiving all the military assistance and economic assistance.",
        "He mentioned that India should understand the betrayal of Sri Lanka and formulate its foreign policy accordingly. (a)"
      ],
